(121, 1, '2025-09-09 19:50:00', '2025-09-09 19:50:00', '<h2>Fresh, Fast &amp; Delicious</h2>				\n		From morning coffee and breakfast to legendary chicken and pizza, we\'ve got your cravings covered.		\n					<h2>Fresh, Fast &amp; Delicious</h2>				\n		Kick off your morning with our delicious breakfast options. Grab a fresh-brewed coffee, a warm breakfast sandwich, or a hearty burrito to fuel your day. Quick, convenient, and always satisfying.		\n					<h2>Quick &amp; Tasty Lunch</h2>				\n		Pressed for time? Our lunch menu is packed with grab-and-go favorites. From fresh sandwiches to hot snacks, we make it easy to enjoy a satisfying meal without the wait.		\n					<h2>Fresh, Fast &amp; Delicious</h2>				\n		We\'ve partnered with the best to bring you the food you love, made fresh for you.		\n															<img width=\"610\" height=\"409\" src=\"http://localhost/faizan_food/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/ecc40e7075af473746badae72fd88e861e27ba2b.png\" alt=\"\" />															\n					<h2>Pizza Your Way</h2>				\n		It\'s All Toppings, No Extra Charge. Order a whole pizza with all your favorite toppings, or grab a Hunk A Pizza for a quick, cheesy slice on the go. Perfect for any meal.		\n					<a href=\"#\">\n									Order it now\n					</a>\n															<img width=\"1024\" height=\"733\" src=\"http://localhost/faizan_food/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/33f800ea2965178a218a389b9e18e483c280b023.png\" alt=\"\" />															\n					<h2>Pizza Your Way</h2>				\n		<p>It\'s All Toppings, No Extra Charge. Order a whole pizza with all your favorite toppings, or grab a Hunk A Pizza for a quick, cheesy slice on the go. Perfect for any meal.</p>		\n					<a href=\"#\">\n									Order it now\n					</a>', 'Our Partners', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'our-partners', '', '', '2025-09-10 23:11:03', '2025-09-10 23:11:03', '', 0, 'http://localhost/faizan_food/?page_id=121', 0, 'page', '', 0),
