(159, 1, '2025-09-10 20:11:49', '2025-09-10 20:11:49', '<h2>FUEL UP AND GET GOING</h2>				\n		Get high-quality gasoline at competitive prices. Our clean, well-lit fuel stations are designed for a quick, safe, and easy stop.		\n					<h2>The Neighbors Market Difference</h2>				\n		<p>At Neighbors Market, we believe your fuel stop should be as pleasant and efficient as your coffee run. We\'re committed to providing not just quality fuel, but a better fueling experience. Our stations are always clean, brightly lit, and equipped with modern, easy-to-use pumps to get you back on your way faster.</p>		\n															<img width=\"720\" height=\"540\" src=\"http://localhost/faizan_food/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/9cb1b646b28f149613ace426919c25d6b004fa95-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" />															\n					<h2>Our Fuel Offerings</h2>				\n		High-Quality Gasoline You Can Trust. Your vehicle is important, and the fuel you put in it matters.		\n							<ul>\n							<li>\n										Regular: High-Quality Gasoline You Can Trust. Your vehicle is important, and the fuel you put in it matters.\n									</li>\n								<li>\n										Plus: A mid-grade option for vehicles that require a little extra performance and protection against engine knock.\n									</li>\n								<li>\n										Premier: Our highest-octane fuel, designed for high-performance engines to maximize power and efficiency.\n									</li>\n								<li>\n										Diesel: High-performance diesel for trucks, fleets, and diesel-engine vehicles, ensuring optimal engine health\n									</li>\n								<li>\n										E85: A high-octane, renewable fuel blend for Flex Fuel Vehicles (FFVs), promoting cleaner emissions.\n									</li>\n						</ul>', 'Fuel', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '117-revision-v1', '', '', '2025-09-10 20:11:49', '2025-09-10 20:11:49', '', 117, 'http://localhost/faizan_food/?p=159', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
